# Empty

A UI placeholder to use when the data is empty or not available. An instruction or friendly message is usually shown here to guide user to the next action.

## Examples

### Basic

The most basic empty template.

```jsx live
<Empty text="Looking for an applicant tracking system? Employment Hero’s ATS software is a robust solution for total employee lifecycle management from Hiring and Onboarding to Off-boarding." />
```

### With extra action

Some action could be added using `extra` prop.

```jsx live
<Empty
  text="Looking for an applicant tracking system? Employment Hero’s ATS software is a robust solution for total employee lifecycle management from Hiring and Onboarding to Off-boarding."
  extra={
    <Button
      icon="add"
      variant="filled"
      intent="primary"
      text="Request a demo"
    />
  }
/>
```

### With title

Empty can be rendered with a title.

```jsx live
<Empty
  extra={
    <Button icon="add" variant="filled" intent="primary" text="Create a goal" />
  }
  title="No goals created yet."
  text="Reach for the stars! Click 'Create a goal' button below to create your first goal."
/>
```

### Sizes

There are two sizes of an Empty: `small` and `medium`.

#### Small size

```jsx live
<Empty
  extra={
    <Button
      icon="add"
      variant="filled"
      intent="primary"
      text="Request a demo"
    />
  }
  text="Looking for an applicant tracking system? Employment Hero’s ATS software is a robust solution for total employee lifecycle management from Hiring and Onboarding to Off-boarding."
  size="small"
/>
```

#### Medium size

```jsx live
<Empty
  extra={
    <Button
      icon="add"
      variant="filled"
      intent="primary"
      text="Request a demo"
    />
  }
  text="Looking for an applicant tracking system? Employment Hero’s ATS software is a robust solution for total employee lifecycle management from Hiring and Onboarding to Off-boarding."
  size="medium"
/>
```

### Customise empty image

By providing imageSrc prop.

```jsx live
<Empty
  imageSrc="data:image/png;base64,"
  extra={
    <Button
      icon="add"
      variant="filled"
      intent="primary"
      text="Request a demo"
    />
  }
  text="Looking for an applicant tracking system? Employment Hero’s ATS software is a robust solution for total employee lifecycle management from Hiring and Onboarding to Off-boarding."
/>
```

### Customise text display

Text prop can be customised as a React element.

```jsx live
<Empty
  extra={
    <Button
      icon="add"
      variant="filled"
      intent="primary"
      text="Request a demo"
    />
  }
  text={
    <Typography.Text>
      Looking for an applicant tracking system?{' '}
      <Button.Link
        href="https://employmenthero.com/product/employment-hero-hr/ats"
        text="Employment Hero’s ATS software"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferer noopener"
      />{' '}
      is a robust solution for total employee lifecycle management from Hiring
      and Onboarding to Off-boarding.
    </Typography.Text>
  }
/>
```
